                    <ab>In nomine domini nosti Iesu Christi die aeterni. <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/110">Hludouuicus</persName> gratia dei
                            <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs> augustus invictissimi domni
                        imperatoris <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/9"
                            >Hlotarii</persName> filius. Dignum est, ut, qui prudenter dei obsequia
                        ordinare procurant et hoc ad stabilitatem perpetuam nostram corroborationem
                        confirmare exposcunt, ut tanto libentius obaudiamus, quanto et deo placita
                        intelligimus et prudentia comite bono studio effectum esse cognoscimus.
                        Quapropter cunctorum fidelium sanctae dei ecclesie ac nostrorum presentium
                        scilicet et futurorum cognoscat sollertia, quia, dum nos dilecto <rs
                            key="#fidelisOf">fideli nostro</rs>
                        <persName key="#fidelisOf" ref="#people/1514">Adalberto</persName>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">coenobium</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/301"
                            key="#Houses #Curtes #Manentes #Cells/hermitages #Monks">domini
                            Saluatoris in <placeName ref="#places/737" key="#Monasteries">monte
                                Amiate</placeName></orgName> constitutum ad regendum commissisemus
                        et ibidem neglecta dei obsequia et procuratione deo ibidem famulantium
                        predecessorum suorum incuria multis modis repperisset, studiosius decertavit
                            <rs key="#Monks">congregationem monachorum</rs> ibidem deo servitium
                        regulariter corrigere et solummodo divinis obsequiis deditos ad
                        sufficientiam suorum largire conferens eis ad sufficientiam suorum <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1512"><placeName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                                ref="#places/1949">cellam sancti Benedicti</placeName></orgName>,
                            <rs key="#Curtes">curte</rs> de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/334"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/764">Palea</placeName></geogName>, <rs
                            key="#Cells/hermitages">cellam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/303">sancti Stephani</orgName> in <placeName
                            ref="#places/757"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Churches"
                            >Monticlo</placeName> et <rs key="#Cells/hermitages">cellam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/302">sancte Marie in <placeName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                                ref="#places/756">Lamulas</placeName></orgName>, <rs key="#Curtes"
                            >curticella</rs> de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/331"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/760">Mustia</placeName></geogName> nec non et
                        curticella de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/335"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/1951">Titinano</placeName></geogName> et in <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Agricultural_workers #Angaria"
                            ref="#places/1952">Cerri</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Agricultural_workers #Angaria">angariales</rs> seu in <placeName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Manentes"
                            ref="#places/761"><geogName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Manentes"
                                ref="#estates/2315">Feroniano</geogName></placeName> et <rs
                            key="#Manentes">manentes</rs> eius nec non et cellam <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/308">sancti Saluatoris</orgName> de <placeName
                            ref="#places/762"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            >Ualerachana</placeName> et <rs key="#Curtes">curticella</rs> de
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/332"><placeName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/1953">Cuniclo</placeName></geogName> cum ipso <rs
                            key="#Houses">cagiolo</rs> de <placeName ref="#places/1953"
                            >Portiano</placeName> et <rs key="#Cells/hermitages">cellam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1455"><placeName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/1948">sancti Stephani</placeName></orgName> in
                            <placeName ref="#places/430"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Churches"
                            >Terquini</placeName> seu et <rs key="#Cells/hermitages">cellam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1513"><placeName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                                ref="#places/1950">sancti Seueri</placeName></orgName> super <rs
                            key="#Lakes">lacu</rs> cum ipso <rs key="#Curtes">culticella</rs> de
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/333"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/1956">Bisentio</placeName></geogName>, <rs
                            key="#Cells/hermitages">cellam</rs> etiam <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1514"><placeName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                                ref="#places/1955">sancti Miniati</placeName></orgName> nec non et
                            <rs key="#Curtes">cortes</rs>, qui vocitantur <geogName
                            key="#Uncertain_tradition #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/1426"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/1954">Corsi</placeName></geogName> et <geogName
                            key="#Uncertain_tradition #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2346"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/1964">Cortiobole</placeName></geogName>, qui sunt de
                            <rs key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/154">Roselense</geogName>, cum
                        omnibus pertinentiis et adiacentiis eorum, ea videlicet ratione, ut ab hinc
                        in futurum predicta sancta congregatio his omnibus denominatis tantummodo
                        suis utilitatibus habentes victum vestitumque regulariter sumentes absque
                        ulla dilatione solummodo divinis die noctuque persistant obsequiis ac pro
                        stabilitate totius imperii nobis a deo commissi studeant exorare. Sed, quod
                        bono studio bonaque voluntate fecit, perennem habeat stabilitatem, petiit
                        pietatem nostram, ut eandem ordinationem nostram confirmaremus
                        conscriptionem, sicuti et fecimus. Quapropter eidem sancto loco hoc nostrum
                        preceptum fieri iussimus, per quod precipimus, ut ab hinc in futurum eadem
                        sanctae congregationi omni quietudine absque ullo publico repetitu auc
                        rectoris loci [i]psius subtractu easdem res in suis utilitatibus ac
                        necessitatibus habeant ordinent et disponant, quatenus exinde sufficientiam
                        habentes in divinis obsequiis nullatenus mittant neglegentiam incuriam, sed
                        eorum assidua famulatio non solum nobis, sed et eidem fideli nostro pro bona
                        ordinatione maneat sempiternale remedium. Ut quoque haec nostrae
                        confirmationis auctoritas pleniorem in dei nomine obtineat vigorem, manu
                        propria subter firmavimus et anuli nostri inpressione adsignari iussimus. Si
                        quis autem, quod absit, ausu temerario infringere ipsum parvipendendo aut
                        annullare temptaverit, debita ab eodem ultione <rs key="#Penalty">centum
                            auri libras</rs> exsolvi indicimus, <rs key="#Camera_regis">medietatem
                            camere nostre</rs> ac <rs key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities"
                            >medietatem predicte abbatie</rs> suisque rectoribus, et perpetuo
                        anathemate in ignea abysso ligetur. Signum (M.) domni Hludouuici serenissimi
                        augusti. (C.) <persName key="#Chancellor"><name ref="Heinricus"
                                >Herincus</name></persName> domni imperatoris <rs key="#Chancellor"
                            >cancellarius</rs> advice <persName ref="#people/3906"
                            >Dructemiri</persName> recognovi et (SR.) (SI. D.) Data IIII non. iulii,
                        anno Christo propicio imperii domni Hlotharii pii augusti XXXIIII et
                        Hludouuici gloriosi imperatoris in Italia IIII, indictione I; actum
                            <placeName ref="#places/65">Papia</placeName> civitate palatio regio; in
                        dei nomine feliciter amen.</ab>
                </div>
